Class GuiController

  • java.lang.Object
    • limmen.id2212.nog.client.view.GuiController

  • public class GuiController
extends Object
    A controller. All calls to the model from the view go through here. All calls from the model to update the view also goes through here.

      • chatRoomDestroyed

        public void chatRoomDestroyed(String creator,
                     int id)
        Method called when a chatroom that the client is present in gets destroyed. This is a method that will update the GUI to reflect the changes. invokeLater to explicit add the event to the EDT since this method will usually get called outside of the EDT.
        Parameters:
        creator - username of the user that destroyed the room
        id - id of the chatroom

      • updateBlocked

        public void updateBlocked(ArrayList<String> blocked)
        Method called when the client list of blocked users have gotten updated. This method will update the GUI to reflect the changes. invokeLater to explicit add the event to the EDT since this method will usually get called outside of the EDT.
        Parameters:
        blocked - the updated list of blocked users.

      • updateMainFrameClients

        public void updateMainFrameClients(ArrayList<Client> clients)

        Parameters:
        clients - list of clients

        Parameters:

      • updateChat

        public void updateChat(ChatRoom r)

        Parameters:

      • successfulRegistration

        public void successfulRegistration(Client client)
        Method called when a attempt to register a client at the server was successful. This method will create a new mainframe to represent the connection to the chatserver. invokeLater to explicit add the event to the EDT since this method will get called from outside the EDT.
        Parameters:
        client - The newly registered client.

      • failedRegistration

        public void failedRegistration(Client client)
        Method called when a attempt to register a client at the server failed because the username already was taken. invokeLater to explicit add the event to the EDT since this method will get called from outside the EDT.
        Parameters:
        client - the client that could'nt be registered.
